release.notes:
Gatefold sleeve. 
Includes an 11-inch booklet and a [url=https://www.discogs.com/release/9074022]Download Card[/url].

© 2016 Third Face, LLC & ℗ 2016 Third Man Records, LLC. Label has these the other way round ℗ 2016 Third Face, LLC, © 2016 Third Man Records, LLC.
All songs remastered 2016 by Andrew Mendelson at Georgetown Masters in Nashville, TN.

Tracks are listed sequentially (regardless of sides) from 1 to 26 on release.

Sticker on sleeve: "The essential Jack White songwriting collection double LP including alternate versions and previously unreleased recordings from The White Stripes, The Raconteurs and solo albums completely remastered".
